<div class="row">
    <div class="text-center light">
        <h1 class="page-header">Lorain County Music Foundation</h1>
        <p>LCMF wishes to provide an outlet for local aspiring & established musicians of all ages, genres & experience levels to perform in a safe & positive environment. 
        Our ultimate goal is to establish a children’s day camp that would provide music therapy for underprivileged & special needs children in the area
        In addition to creating a day camp for kids, we plan to begin a program with the local high schools & colleges to help students to earn school credit by volunteering  & doing something they love…all while building their skills & finishing their degree.
        </p>
        <hr>
    </div>
</div>
